Package: classR
Title: A Minimal GitHub Classroom Replacement in R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Cristian", "Roman Palacios", email = "cromanpa@arizona.edu",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Runs a course on GitHub from R without GitHub Classroom. Each
    student gets a new private repository in an organization with a set of
    starter files. The student is added as a collaborator.
